<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 rén shì zhōng guó rén, hún shì zhōng guó hún, xīn shì zhōng guó xīn, yīn shì zhōng guó yīn.
 huǒ de shí dài cuī cù wǒ men zǒu, méi yǒu wàng jì zì jǐ shì yī gè zhōng guó rén.
 zhōng guó de jiào huì yào xíng zhēn lǐ, zhōng guó de jiào huì yào guǎng chuán fú yīn,
 huǒ de shí dài cuī cù wǒ men zǒu méi yǒu wàng jì zì jǐ shì yī gè zhōng guó rén.
 ràng zhōng guó jiào huì chéng wèi shén de jiā, zhè shì wǒ men yì bù róng cí de zé rèn.
 ràng zhōng guó jiào huì xiàng zhe zhēn lǐ zǒu, zhè shì wǒ men jiān shàng zuì dà de zhòng rèn,
 zhè shì wǒ men jiān shàng zuì dà de zhòng rèn,</lyrics>
<title>rén shì zhōng guó rén 迦南469</title>
